column5: Thanks for all the nice wishes guys and gals...  And Maureen...  No heart failure...Heartburn maybe !...  And as far as taking the day off...you are all heart seeing as every day is a day off when I am retired...
hope you had a great day!Little bit late seeing this.Happy Birthday.
I know I'm Late Norm...  HAPPY BIRTHDAY..My Friend
Not as late as I Kelvin.  But I hope you're celebrating right through the weekend Norm.

Happy Birthday Norm, and congratulations on lasting so long,   I thought I would have given you heart failure by now  :whistling:   hope you enjoy your day...as a matter of fact, why don't you take the day off...  Maureen
Happy Birthday my friend and all the best to ya !!
